<h2 class="wsite-content-title" style="text-align:center;">Homestay Details</h2>

<div class="paragraph" style="text-align:center;"><span style="color:rgb(0, 0, 0)">Wildflower Homestay if you want to recall and experience Stone Age stay in the forest then this is the perfect choice.&nbsp;</span><span style="color:rgb(0, 0, 0)">Many consider&nbsp;</span><strong style="color:rgb(0, 0, 0)">Dandeli wildlife reserve</strong><span style="color:rgb(0, 0, 0)">&nbsp;in Karnataka to be one of the most beautiful forests in India. WildFlower Homestay</span><strong style="color:rgb(0, 0, 0)">&nbsp;</strong><span style="color:rgb(0, 0, 0)">&nbsp;borders Dandeli reserve forest and is situated in a unique and beautiful location. Nestled amongst thick forest at the foothills of the breathtakingly beautiful Dandeli jungle bell camp site ideal ambience to come, unwind and be one with nature.</span><span style="color:rgb(0, 0, 0)">The camp is surrounded by lush green forest on three sides and the where you will find animals grazing in peace, presenting you with a perfect opportunity to watch them in their habitat from the comfort and safety from camp site forest stream on the other side makes this camp truly exceptional and offers complete privacy, comfort and tranquility. Activities White water Rafting, Rappelling, Rock Climbing, River Crossing, Kayaking, Coracle Ride, Jeep Safari.<br /></span><br /><font size="4" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><strong>Activities</strong></font><br /><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">Whitewater rafting, River crossing, Kayaking , Jacuzzi Bath, Coracle Ride, Sight Seeing, Jeep Safari and Night Camping.</span><br /><br /><font size="4" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><strong>Spots around the resort</strong></font><br /><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">Vantage Point to view Supa Dam, Crocodile viewing on River Kali, Syntheri Rocks, Kavala Caves, Coconut and Banana plantations, Skyes Point</span><span style="color:rgb(0, 0, 0)"><br />&#8203;</span><br /></div>
